      <title>中国建筑商雅居乐首次对美元债券违约</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-14/chinese-builder-agile-defaults-for-first-time-on-dollar-bonds</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国别墅公寓和高层住宅开发商雅居乐集团控股有限公司(Agile Group Holdings Ltd.)首次公开发行的美元债券出现违约，凸显了在中国前所未有的房地产危机中挥之不去的困境。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-14/chinese-builder-agile-defaults-for-first-time-on-dollar-bonds</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 14 May 2024 00:09:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
